## 3. Tipografia

### Famílias

- **Display/Headings:** Inter, system-ui, sans-serif
- **Body:** Inter, system-ui, sans-serif
- **Monospace/Labels:** JetBrains Mono, Fira Code, monospace

### Escala Tipográfica

| Elemento | Tamanho | Weight | Letter-spacing | Line-height |
|----------|---------|--------|----------------|-------------|
| H1 (Hero) | 96px | **700** | -0.03em | 1.0 |
| H2 (Section) | 48px | 700 | -0.02em | 1.1 |
| H3 (Project) | 32px | 600 | -0.01em | 1.2 |
| H4 (Card) | 24px | 600 | 0 | 1.3 |
| H5 (Subtitle) | 18px | 500 | 0 | 1.4 |
| H6 (Label) | 14px | 600 | 0.05em | 1.4 |
| Body Large | 18px | 400 | 0 | 1.6 |
| Body | 16px | 400 | 0 | 1.6 |
| Body Small | 14px | 400 | 0 | 1.5 |
| Caption | 12px | 400 | 0.01em | 1.4 |
| Micro/Mono | 12px | 500 | 0.1em | 1.2 |

### Responsividade

- **Mobile (<640px):** H1: 48px, H2: 32px, H3: 24px
- **Tablet (640-1024px):** H1: 64px, H2: 40px, H3: 28px
- **Desktop (>1024px):** H1: 96px, H2: 48px, H3: 32px

**Regras:** H1 pode usar gradient text com #471bf6 (opcional). Font-weight nunca abaixo de 400.

---

## 4. Espaçamento & Grid

### Sistema (Base 8px)

`--space-1` a `--space-11`: 4px → 160px

### Grid

- Container max-width: 1200px
- Padding: 24px (mobile) / 48px (desktop)
- Column gap: 24px (desktop) / 16px (mobile)
- Row gap: 48px

### Breakpoints

`--bp-sm: 640px` | `--bp-md: 768px` | `--bp-lg: 1024px` | `--bp-xl: 1280px` | `--bp-2xl: 1536px`

### Seções

- Section padding vertical: 96px–160px
- Hero: 100vh ou min-height 800px
- Cards: padding 24–32px, border-radius **12px**

---

## 5. Componentes UI

### Botões

**Primary:** `bg-[#471bf6]`, text white, padding 12px 24px, rounded-lg, font 600 uppercase. Box-shadow glow. Hover: `bg-[#5a35f7]`, translateY(-2px), shadow maior. Active: shadow inset.

**Secondary:** Transparent, border 1px `#471bf6`, text `#471bf6`. Hover: `bg-[#2a1266]`, border `#5a35f7`.

**Ghost:** Transparent, text `text-secondary`. Hover: text `#471bf6`, underline animado.

### Cards

**Project Card:** `bg-[#12121a]`, border `#1e1e2e`, rounded-xl. Hover: translateY(-4px), border `rgba(71,27,246,0.3)`, shadow + glow. Image 16/9, content padding 24px.

**Stat Card:** Border sutil, text-align center. Número H2 `#471bf6`, label caption uppercase.

**Feature Card:** Ícone 40px com `primary` e `primary-subtle`. Title H5, description body small.

### Links

- **Text Link:** Cor `#471bf6`, font-weight 500. Hover: `#5a35f7`. Underline ::after 2px.
- **Nav Link:** `text-secondary`, hover `text-primary`. Active: `#471bf6` com dot/underline.

### Tags/Badges

**Tech Tag:** `bg-[#1e1e2e]`, padding 4px 12px, monospace. Hover: border `rgba(71,27,246,0.3)`.

**Tech Tag destacada:** `bg-[#2a1266]`, `#5a35f7`, border `rgba(71,27,246,0.3)`.

**Status Badge:** Online (success-subtle), Offline (error-subtle). Indicator 8px, pulse para online.

### Inputs

Background `#12121a`, border `#1e1e2e`, rounded-lg. Focus: border `#471bf6`, shadow `0 0 0 3px rgba(71,27,246,0.15)`.

