## 6. Animações & Interações

**Princípios:** Feedback com propósito. Preferir `transform` e `opacity`. Duração 150–300ms. `prefers-reduced-motion`.

**Durações:** fast 150ms | normal 200ms | slow 300ms | slower 500ms

**Easing:** default `cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)` | spring `(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1)`

**Animações:** Fade In Up | Scale In | Underline Grow | Card Lift + glow | **Glow Pulse** | **Gradient Shift** (hero)

**Scroll:** Sticky header com `backdrop-blur` e `rgba(10,10,15,0.8)` quando scrolled.

**Performance:** Glows com `box-shadow`, não `filter: drop-shadow`.

---

## 7. Seções Específicas

### Hero

Layout full viewport, flex column justify-center. Micro-label mono `#471bf6` → H1 96px bold → headline 48px `text-secondary` → CTAs. Background `#0a0a0f` + radial-gradient topo com primary-glow. Opcional: gradient text H1.

### Projects

Zig-zag, gap 96px. Label "CASE STUDY 01" em `#471bf6` → Title H3 → Description → Solution → Metrics em `#471bf6` → Tags → Links `#471bf6`.

### Stack

Grid 3 col. Icon hover `#471bf6`. Barra progresso fill `#471bf6`.

### About

2 col, gap 48px. Photo border hover `#471bf6`. Pillars ícones `#471bf6`. Timeline dots `#471bf6`.

### Contact

Centered max-width 600px. Headline "Vamos construir algo juntos?". Links cards hover border `#471bf6` e glow. Terminal fake prompt `#471bf6`.

---

## 8. Assets & Mídia

**Imagens:** WebP < 200KB, lazy loading. Tons frios/neutros. Overlays com primary-glow opcional.

**Ícones:** Lucide React. Tamanhos 16/20/24/32px. Hover `#471bf6`.

**Meta:** Favicon SVG `#471bf6`. OG 1200x630 fundo escuro, texto violet e branco. Theme-color `#0a0a0f`.

---

## 9. Acessibilidade

- Contraste 4.5:1 (#471bf6 sobre fundos)
- Focus outline `#471bf6` ou branco, 2px offset
- Skip link, alt text, aria-label
- `prefers-reduced-motion`
- Semântica: header, nav, main, section, footer

---

## 10. Performance (1GB RAM)

- Static export, font-display swap, Tailwind purge
- Glows: `box-shadow` em vez de filter
- Budgets: FCP < 1.5s | TTI < 3.5s | Bundle < 200KB | Lighthouse > 90

