// Button Primary
bg-[#471bf6] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider hover:bg-[#5a35f7] hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(71,27,246,0.3)] hover:shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(71,27,246,0.4)]

// Button Secondary
